## Error Handling

### Validation Errors

| Error Code | HTTP Status | Scenario | Message |
|------------|-------------|----------|---------|
| 109_40018 | 400 | Empty file | "Migration file is empty. Please upload a valid Excel file." |
| 109_40019 | 400 | Invalid format | "Invalid file format. Please upload an Excel file (.xlsx or .xls)." |
| 109_40020 | 400 | Unsupported type | "Unsupported migration type: '{type}'. Supported types: {list}." |
| 109_40021 | 400 | No records | "No records found in the Excel file. Please check the file content." |
| 109_40022 | 400 | File too large | "File size exceeds maximum allowed size of {size} MB." |

### Processing Errors

| Error Code | HTTP Status | Scenario | Message |
|------------|-------------|----------|---------|
| 109_50018 | 500 | Parse failure | "Failed to parse migration file: {details}" |
| 109_50019 | 500 | Processing failure | "Error processing migration data: {details}" |

### Error Handling Flow

```
Request → Validation → Processing → Response
   ↓          ↓            ↓
  Error    Error        Error
   ↓          ↓            ↓
GlobalApiExceptionHandler
   ↓
Structured Error Response
```

