## Testing

### Unit Testing

**Test the Factory:**

```java
@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension.class)
class MigrationProcessorFactoryTest {
    
    @Mock
    private ParchmentMigrationProcessor parchmentProcessor;
    
    @InjectMocks
    private MigrationProcessorFactory factory;
    
    @Test
    void shouldReturnParchmentProcessor() {
        when(parchmentProcessor.supports("parchment")).thenReturn(true);
        
        MigrationProcessor processor = factory.getProcessor("parchment");
        
        assertNotNull(processor);
        assertEquals("parchment", processor.getMigrationType());
    }
    
    @Test
    void shouldThrowExceptionForUnsupportedType() {
        assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, 
            () -> factory.getProcessor("unknown"));
    }
}
```

**Test the Controller:**

```java
